    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but why not honey though? i've read so many things about medical grade honey being used in hospitals for wound healing. if it's good enough for them, couldn't i just use it at home to stop the oozing and prevent infection? it seems way easier than waiting hours at a doctor's office just for a tiny cut.",
