      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i get that but i actually have some manuka honey in the pantry right now... i checked the label and it says it's high quality. if i use that, and just wrap it really tight with a clean gauze, do you think that would be safe enough to just let it heal on its own? it's really deep and i'm just worried about the possibility of infection if i don't treat it immediately with something natural.",
